              <h3 id="upload-reference-images-or-shapes" class="heading-m">Upload reference images or shapes.</h3>
              <p class="body-l">Upload an image whose style you want to replicate, for example, create a white 3D sphere on a blue background. Then build on that structure to generate similar shapes like basketballs, soccer balls or anything round you can imagine.</p>
