          <div class="foreground">
            <div class="body-m">
              <h2 id="faqs-about-ai-image-generator" class="heading-xl">FAQs about AI image generator.</h2>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-container seo con-block max-width-10-desktop" data-block-status="loaded" data-block=""><div class="descr-list accordion foreground" id="accordion-1" role="presentation"><div class="descr-term"><h3 class="accordion-heading"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-1" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-1" daa-ll="open-1--What is text to image in AI">
            
              What is text to image in AI?
            
          <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></h3></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-1" id="accordion-1-content-1" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>Text to image is a type of generative AI technology that lets you create images with nothing more than a few words. The AI engine receives each word in a text description as an instruction, and it builds the image based on the combination of words and their relationships to one another.</div></div><div class="descr-term"><h3 class="accordion-heading"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-2" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-2" daa-ll="open-2--How does text to image work">
            
              How does text to image work?
            
          <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></h3></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-2" id="accordion-1-content-2" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>Text to image AI generators work like other types of artificial intelligence, using machine learning models and huge datasets to produce their results. In other words, the AI technology learns from thousands and thousands of pictures. It creates brand-new images by applying what it has learned to the everyday language you enter in the prompt field. The current Firefly generative AI model is trained on a dataset of Adobe Stock, along with openly licensed work and public domain content where copyright has expired.</div></div><div class="descr-term"><h3 class="accordion-heading"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-3" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-3" daa-ll="open-3--What makes an amazing AI image generator">
            
              What makes an amazing AI image generator?
            
          <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></h3></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-3" id="accordion-1-content-3" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>When choosing your AI image generator, look for one that produces high-quality images, allows you creative control to make those images fit your needs, and makes it possible to use those images commercially. Firefly is a great choice because it does all these things.</div></div><div class="descr-term"><h3 class="accordion-heading"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-4" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-4" daa-ll="open-4--Are Firefly images available for commercial use">
            
              Are Firefly images available for commercial use?
            
          <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></h3></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-4" id="accordion-1-content-4" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>Yes, you can commercially use images generated with Firefly features that are out of beta. You can also use images generated with Firefly features still in beta, unless explicitly stated otherwise in the product or in a specific agreement with Adobe.</div></div><div class="descr-term"><h3 class="accordion-heading"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-5" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-5" daa-ll="open-5--Do I own the copyright to the images I generate in Firefly">
            
              Do I own the copyright to the images I generate in Firefly?
            
          <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></h3></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-5" id="accordion-1-content-5" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>This will depend on the laws of your local jurisdiction. If you are interested in learning more copyright, check out <a href="https://copyrightalliance.org/protecting-creators-generative-ai/">this blog post</a> by Adobe’s lead copyright attorney.</div></div><div class="descr-term"><h3 class="accordion-heading"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-6" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-6" daa-ll="open-6--What is an AI image generator">
            
              What is an AI image generator?
            
          <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></h3></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-6" id="accordion-1-content-6" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>An AI image generator allows users to enter simple inputs (such as a text prompt) to create visual imagery. Adobe Firefly is an example of an AI image generator with a text-to-image feature. Generative AI models are often trained on large amounts of wide-ranging visual data that form the basis of how it “learns” to generate imagery based on various styles, patterns, and contexts.</div></div><div class="descr-term"><h3 class="accordion-heading"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-7" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-7" daa-ll="open-7--Is Adobe Firefly s online AI image generator free to use">
            
              Is Adobe Firefly's online AI image generator free to use?
            
          <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></h3></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-7" id="accordion-1-content-7" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>Yes, you can use the AI image generator for free with an Adobe account. Free users receive a set number of monthly generative credits.</div></div><div class="descr-term"><h3 class="accordion-heading"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-8" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-8" daa-ll="open-8--Can I edit the images created by the AI picture generator">
            
              Can I edit the images created by the AI picture generator?
            
          <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></h3></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-8" id="accordion-1-content-8" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>Once generated, you can download the images and edit them using your preferred design tools or regenerate variations directly within Firefly.</div></div><div class="descr-term"><h3 class="accordion-heading"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-9" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-9" daa-ll="open-9--Can I generate images in Adobe Firefly using Nano Banana">
            
              Can I generate images in Adobe Firefly using Nano Banana?
            
          <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></h3></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-9" id="accordion-1-content-9" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>Yes. Nano banana is available as a partner model for image generation in Adobe Firefly. You can access it through the Text to Image module by selecting Gemini 2.5 Flash Image from the model dropdown menu.</div></div><div class="descr-term"><h3 class="accordion-heading"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-10" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-10" daa-ll="open-10--Why is Firefly the best text to picture generator">
            
              Why is Firefly the best text to picture generator?
            
          <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></h3></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-10" id="accordion-1-content-10" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>The best AI text to picture generator is the one that gives you high-quality results without sacrificing creative control. Firefly makes this possible with intuitive tools that help you go from a simple prompt to a polished visual in a matter of seconds. Every image is created with commercial use in mind, and you can refine lighting, style, color, and composition to ensure the final output fits your project’s exact vision. With fast results, flexible controls, and professional-grade quality, Firefly makes it easy to create images that meet your needs every time.</div></div><div class="descr-term"><h3 class="accordion-heading"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-11" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-11" daa-ll="open-11--How do I craft the perfect AI image prompt">
            
              How do I craft the perfect AI image prompt?
            
          <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></h3></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-11" id="accordion-1-content-11" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>Great prompts start with clear creative direction. To get the best results, include specific details across the core categories, including subject and action, style and medium, environment, lighting, and composition. These elements guide the AI model toward your intended mood, visual style, and level of detail. When your prompt covers these foundations, Firefly can quickly generate high-quality images that line up with your creative vision.</div></div><div class="descr-term"><h3 class="accordion-heading"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-12" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-12" daa-ll="open-12--What are the best AI text to picture generators available">
            
              What are the best AI text to picture generators available?
            
          <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></h3></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-12" id="accordion-1-content-12" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>Adobe Firefly integrates top AI Text to image generators, allowing users to switch between partner models such as Gemini 2.5 Flash Image, Flux 1.1, and GPT Image via the Model dropdown in General Settings. This allows users to leverage specialized capabilities, such as high-resolution detail or photorealism, within their existing Text to image workflow.</div></div></div></div>
